    if (Q.zhili_opposition < 0) {
        Q.zhili_opposition = 0;
    }

    Q.zhili_antiwar_concession_2 = 1

!}
subtitle: This concession is already well liked by some of the pragmatists, though it can legitimize this course of action with moderates, possibly making it harder to pull out in the future without a good reason.
view-if: zhili_antiwar == 1
choose-if: zhili_antiwar_concession_2 == 0   
